{
  "id": "60803aecd86bb1001c3561fc",
  "title": "アイコン記法を一人称にする",
  "created": 1619016432,
  "updated": 1713306580,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "60803aecd86bb1001c3561fc",
      "text": "アイコン記法を一人称にする",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619016432,
      "updated": 1619016435
    },
    {
      "id": "60803af3e5172d000068a63d",
      "text": "\t例：[yosider.icon]は今日も元気です",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619016435,
      "updated": 1619016446
    },
    {
      "id": "60803afee5172d000068a63f",
      "text": "\t利点",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619016446,
      "updated": 1619016452
    },
    {
      "id": "60803b03e5172d000068a640",
      "text": "\t　[一人称]を悩まなくてすむ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619016452,
      "updated": 1619016501
    },
    {
      "id": "60803cc61280f00000b7c7a2",
      "text": "\t　主語を明確にできる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619016901,
      "updated": 1619016916
    },
    {
      "id": "608e40d0db62ad0000011a9e",
      "text": "\t　検索しやすい",
      "userId": "5b8d55ab7d11180014db62ad",
      "created": 1619935440,
      "updated": 1619935444
    },
    {
      "id": "60803b10e5172d000068a642",
      "text": "\t欠点",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619016464,
      "updated": 1619016466
    },
    {
      "id": "60803b12e5172d000068a643",
      "text": "\t　[一人称が自分のファーストネーム]の人みたいに見える？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619016467,
      "updated": 1619016487
    },
    {
      "id": "608df06f8ee92a0000adc2c2",
      "text": " \t　見えないと思う... [増井俊之.icon][dnin.icon][sta.icon][takker.icon][yanma.icon]",
      "userId": "5b8d55ab7d11180014db62ad",
      "created": 1619914863,
      "updated": 1619935439
    },
    {
      "id": "608e40521280f0000030dc54",
      "text": "\t　 アイコン記法をファーストネームで脳内音読することがない[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619935316,
      "updated": 1619935355
    },
    {
      "id": "661edc61b8bbfc0000263611",
      "text": "\t　 見えてるよ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1713298529,
      "updated": 1713298532
    },
    {
      "id": "60803af5e5172d000068a63e",
      "text": "\t\tAさんが`「Bさんは～～と言っていた」`のB部分をアイコン記法にしたときに、一瞬Bさんの発言だと空目する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619016437,
      "updated": 1619935050
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3f0879d3a9000062d85b",
      "text": "\t\t\tよく見たらわかるので大した問題ではないか[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1619934986,
      "updated": 1619934993
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3ee279d3a9000062d85a",
      "text": "   e.g.",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619934947,
      "updated": 1619935165
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3fbb1280f0000030dc50",
      "text": "    [貞子.icon]は~~と言っていた[user1.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619935165,
      "updated": 1619935166
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3f8b1280f0000030dc4e",
      "text": "     `言っていた`とついているから空目しないかな[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619935117,
      "updated": 1619935167
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3fc179d3a9000062d85d",
      "text": "     \t`(アイコン)`の次に`は`が来ると、一人称じゃない使い方だなと判断できるかも",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1619935171,
      "updated": 1619935195
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3fe079d3a9000062d85e",
      "text": "     \tいや、普通に「僕は」的な書き方するか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1619935202,
      "updated": 1619935208
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3fe779d3a9000062d85f",
      "text": "     \t\te.g. [sta.icon]はカルビが好きです",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1619935208,
      "updated": 1619935220
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3f9f1280f0000030dc4f",
      "text": "    [yosider.icon]は今日も元気です[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619935137,
      "updated": 1619935173
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3fc41280f0000030dc51",
      "text": "     これは空目しそう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619935174,
      "updated": 1619935186
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3fd11280f0000030dc52",
      "text": "     「[yosider.icon]は今日も元気です」だけなら、[yosider.icon]さんの発言になるが",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619935187,
      "updated": 1619935234
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3ffa1280f0000030dc53",
      "text": "     後ろに[takker.icon]をつけた途端、[takker.icon]の伝聞になる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619935227,
      "updated": 1619935292
    },
    {
      "id": "608e6e98e5172d00004ac026",
      "text": "    [貞子.icon][高枝切りばさみ.icon][日付入れ太郎.icon]ワタシタチハイツモソバニイルヨ[日記.icon][芝刈り機.icon][user1.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619947160,
      "updated": 1619947275
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3f241280f0000030dc4d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619935013,
      "updated": 1619935013
    },
    {
      "id": "60803cee1280f00000b7c7a4",
      "text": "よく使う[takker.icon][yosider.icon][sk6cleine.icon][45Nuyagawa.icon]",
      "userId": "5d131fa66fe2890017055332",
      "created": 1619016942,
      "updated": 1633965551
    },
    {
      "id": "6163cc270553320000df611d",
      "text": "\t便利～～",
      "userId": "5d131fa66fe2890017055332",
      "created": 1633930280,
      "updated": 1633930282
    },
    {
      "id": "60803ceb1280f00000b7c7a3",
      "text": "二人が使うの見て最近たまに使うになった[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1619016938,
      "updated": 1619935315
    },
    {
      "id": "608e3f1f79d3a9000062d85c",
      "text": "便利なんだけど、[ニュースピーク]のような気がして、使い方について悩んでいる[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1619935008,
      "updated": 1633944928
    },
    {
      "id": "616405175b98c200004bc5dd",
      "text": "「自分」と打つよりcmd + iのほうが早いので便利かも？[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1633944855,
      "updated": 1633947785
    },
    {
      "id": "6164108e774b170000f43723",
      "text": " 最後につければいいか[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1633947790,
      "updated": 1633947798
    },
    {
      "id": "61641096774b170000f43725",
      "text": "  例：今日も元気です[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1633947798,
      "updated": 1633947814
    },
    {
      "id": "661edc6db8bbfc0000263612",
      "text": "しばしば[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1713298542,
      "updated": 1713298546
    },
    {
      "id": "61641081774b170000f43722",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1633947777,
      "updated": 1633947777
    },
    {
      "id": "60803b2fe5172d000068a645",
      "text": "#アイコン記法",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619016495,
      "updated": 1619016498
    },
    {
      "id": "661efb3f71b3c20000461544",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306423,
      "updated": 1713306423
    },
    {
      "id": "60803b2fe5172d000068a646",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1619016495,
      "updated": 1713306419
    },
    {
      "id": "661efb0971b3c20000461542",
      "text": "元タイトル「一人称としてicon記法を使う」です",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306368,
      "updated": 1713306426
    },
    {
      "id": "661efb1c71b3c20000461543",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306388,
      "updated": 1713306418
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c2000046152e",
      "text": "[who5.icon]は賛成ですみたいな使い方",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c2000046152f",
      "text": "行末にアイコンを書かなくてもいいし、文脈的にだれかわかりやすい",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461530",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461531",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]はたまにこの記法を使いたくなる",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461532",
      "text": "\t一人称を使うときに話が込み入ってそうな時に[Summer498.icon]はって言いたくなる",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461533",
      "text": "\t\tそうそう。私って書くと文末まで目を動かさないとだれかわからないけど、[bsahd.icon]は賛成ですって書けばすぐ誰かわかるし、一文が複数人になってもいい。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461535",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461536",
      "text": "\t文脈を読み取るのは特殊能力[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461537",
      "text": " \t一人称としてicon記法を使うかつ文末アイコン記法を使わないときと一人称としてicon記法を使わないかつ文末アイコン記法を使うときとで誰かの判別法が変わる",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461538",
      "text": " \t文の主語をわかりたいときと書き込んだ人をわかりたいときとで差異がある",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efba571b3c20000461546",
      "text": " \t\t[bsahd.icon]は賛成です",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306525,
      "updated": 1713306531
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461539",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c2000046153a",
      "text": "私とか俺だと、年齢とか性別みたいな余計なペルソナを感じてしまうけれど、アイコンだと識別できる\"I\"といった感じで雑念なく文章を読めるので好き[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c2000046153b",
      "text": "\tまあ実際ctrl+\"I\"なのでね[bsahd.icon]やばいWindowsがばれる",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c2000046153c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efbc971b3c20000461548",
      "text": "日本語はもともと一人称がかなり多いのにさらにicon記法という一人称が増えるのか",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306560,
      "updated": 1713306580
    },
    {
      "id": "661efbc871b3c20000461547",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306559,
      "updated": 1713306559
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c2000046153d",
      "text": "[アイコン記法を一人称にする]が再生産されている[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c2000046153e",
      "text": "\t統合しときます[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c2000046153f",
      "text": "\t\t語順逆ぅ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461540",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    },
    {
      "id": "661efaef71b3c20000461541",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1713306343,
      "updated": 1713306343
    }
  ]
}